[
    {
        "text": "Today I'm answering your questions about the P sound sounding like a B.",
        "start": 0.2,
        "duration": 4.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Every once in a while, I get a question about the P sound sounding like a B.",
        "start": 9.28,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, people have asked about the words: spoon, rapport, and pepper.",
        "start": 13.92,
        "duration": 5.86
    },
    {
        "text": "And I know that some teachers teach that these Ps should be a B.",
        "start": 19.78,
        "duration": 5.04
    },
    {
        "text": "I disagree with that.",
        "start": 24.82,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's talk about why.",
        "start": 26.42,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "The thing is, it's not about this sound being a P or B.",
        "start": 28.42,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "It's about the sound being very light.",
        "start": 32.82,
        "duration": 3.42
    },
    {
        "text": "If you make the P light, it sounds great.",
        "start": 36.24,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "If you make the B light, it sounds almost the same.",
        "start": 39.3,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Also good.",
        "start": 42.84,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "But if you make the B sound heavy: sboon-- it doesn't sound so good anymore.",
        "start": 44.0,
        "duration": 6.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Sboon.",
        "start": 50.34,
        "duration": 1.38
    },
    {
        "text": "So it's not about changing the P to a B.",
        "start": 51.72,
        "duration": 3.02
    },
    {
        "text": "It's about knowing how to make a light P.",
        "start": 54.74,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "If someone makes the P sound by itself, it sounds like this.",
        "start": 58.42,
        "duration": 4.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Pphh--- phh--- phh---",
        "start": 63.12,
        "duration": 4.42
    },
    {
        "text": "It's over exaggerated. In a word, that's not how we actually do it.",
        "start": 67.54,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "So if people think that 'Pphh--' is the P sound, then ‘spoon’ would be: spoon.",
        "start": 72.26,
        "duration": 7.28
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's not how we pronounce that word.",
        "start": 79.54,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "It's not: spoon— spoon—",
        "start": 82.46,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "It's also not: sboon— sboon—",
        "start": 86.14,
        "duration": 4.12
    },
    {
        "text": "The right sound is: spoon— spoon— a light P that releases directly into the vowel.",
        "start": 90.26,
        "duration": 8.2
    },
    {
        "text": "So how do we get this light P?",
        "start": 98.46,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to change the idea. P is not pphh---",
        "start": 100.9,
        "duration": 3.9
    },
    {
        "text": "P is p- p- p- p- much lighter a much smaller release.",
        "start": 104.8,
        "duration": 7.8
    },
    {
        "text": "Spoon. Poon— poon— spoon— spoon—",
        "start": 112.6,
        "duration": 12.16
    },
    {
        "text": "We go right from the release into the vowel without pphh-- hh-- hh-- all of this extra air.",
        "start": 124.76,
        "duration": 7.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Spoon— spoon—",
        "start": 132.2,
        "duration": 5.96
    },
    {
        "text": "pe— pepper— pepper—",
        "start": 138.16,
        "duration": 4.58
    },
    {
        "text": "A light feeling in the P, not too much air: pphh--",
        "start": 142.74,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Right now, try this out loud with me:",
        "start": 146.88,
        "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
        "text": "sp-- sp-- spoon— spoon—",
        "start": 152.28,
        "duration": 9.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's do some more words.",
        "start": 161.36,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Pe— per— pepper— pepper—",
        "start": 164.64,
        "duration": 8.02
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you practicing out loud? Please do.",
        "start": 172.66,
        "duration": 3.34
    },
    {
        "text": "Pepper— pepper—",
        "start": 176.0,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Awww. My dog growing up was named Pepper.",
        "start": 178.6,
        "duration": 4.2
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a picture of me and Pepper.",
        "start": 182.8,
        "duration": 4.02
    },
    {
        "text": "P- p- Port— port—",
        "start": 186.82,
        "duration": 5.54
    },
    {
        "text": "report— report—",
        "start": 192.36,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Pam— sp— spam—",
        "start": 196.76,
        "duration": 6.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Spam—",
        "start": 202.92,
        "duration": 5.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Sp-- spam—",
        "start": 208.32,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Span-- sp--",
        "start": 212.72,
        "duration": 8.22
    },
    {
        "text": "speed—",
        "start": 220.94,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "speed—",
        "start": 223.66,
        "duration": 5.66
    },
    {
        "text": "pen—",
        "start": 229.32,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "spin—",
        "start": 231.48,
        "duration": 2.86
    },
    {
        "text": "spin—",
        "start": 234.34,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "pace—",
        "start": 237.06,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "space—",
        "start": 238.9,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "space—",
        "start": 241.38,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "Sp-- pell—",
        "start": 243.96,
        "duration": 3.48
    },
    {
        "text": "spell—",
        "start": 247.44,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "spell—",
        "start": 249.56,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "So don't try to change the P sound to a B.",
        "start": 251.4,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Just make sure you're making it a light sound and you'll sound great.",
        "start": 255.18,
        "duration": 4.82
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're not sure about the sounds of American English,",
        "start": 260.0,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "check out this playlist here.",
        "start": 263.12,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "I've made a video for each sound.",
